README for Game of Life (Lisp)
==============================

This is an open source (MIT license) version of John Conway's "Game of Life" written in Common Lisp by Mikko Saarela.

The development was done in CLisp.

Usage:

	(load "game.lisp")
	(load "unit-tests.lisp")

To display the grid currently:
	(print-grid) 

To initialize the grid with a test shape:
	(test-shape)

To calculate the next generation:
	(apply-deltas (tick))
